name: CROISSANT CUTTER
description: Which of the croissant would you prefer? The soft fluffy buttery or the lava chocolate? I love them all but I have to say the best sound is when a sharp knife crush all the layers in the Croissant. Yes, I know a saint person wont cut Croissant with a knife. Only an inner psychopath does that..but don't you want to hear that Crunch sound?
